>   
>  <span data-ttu-id="f979d-134">`LOB`仅当关闭连接时才关闭临时，但在加载时，临时 `LOB` 不会关闭。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f979d-134">Temporary `LOB`s are only closed when the connection is closed, but with pooling and under load, temporary `LOB`s do not close.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f979d-135">这可以通过调用来释放临时的来解决 `LOB` `tempLob.Dispose()` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f979d-135">This can be resolved by disposing the temporary `LOB`, by invoking `tempLob.Dispose()`.</span></span>

  
  
